column5: My dad and i were thinking of going up to Bellwood in furgus for some shore fishing but do not want to go when the pike tourney is going on could someone please tell me when it ends?  Thanks very much  -[L.A]-
the belwood derby is next saturday and sunday. bpsbassman from the board here was mentioning that there was a toonie tournament there, believe it was today, from 7am -3pm  hope it helps  ryan
Someone get this kid a calendar with important fishing dates.  forrest
